Bayan da aladu suka ci wani manomi a Oregon a shekara ta 2012, wani manomi a Manitoba ya gaya wa CBC News cewa aladu ba sa yawan faɗa, amma ƙanshin jini yana iya zama mai saurin ɓoyewa.
