Yan sanda sun kama Dyton Simpson wanda ake zargi da kisan dan wasan LSU
'Yan sanda sun kama wani da ake zargi da yin amfani da bindiga wajen kashe Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwando mai shekara 20 a LSU.
An kama Dyteon Simpson mai shekara 20 kuma an tsare shi a gidan yari bisa laifin kisan kai, in ji 'yan sanda a garin Baton Rouge.
Jami'an 'yan sanda sun fitar da bidiyon da ke nuna yadda Sims da Simpson suka yi faɗa, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a wannan rikici.
