Bayan sun yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya amsa laifinsa na harbe Wayde da kuma kashe shi.
An nemi a ba da belin dalar Amurka 350,000.
Ofishin kula da lafiyar mutane na gabashin Baton Rouge ya fitar da rahoton farko a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce dalilin mutuwar shi ne wata wuka da aka harbe kansa a wuyansa.
Hukumar 'yan sanda ta gode wa hukumar 'yan sanda ta jihar Louisiana, da hukumar bincike kan masu tserewa, da jami'an 'yan sanda na jihar, da jami'an 'yan sanda na jami'ar Southern da kuma mazauna yankin da suka taimaka wajen gudanar da bincike da ya kai ga kama mutumin.
Daraktan wasanni na LSU Joe Alleva ya gode wa hukumomin karamar hukuma da suka tabbatar da dokar ta dace da kuma neman gaskiya.
Sims yana da shekaru 20.
