Wani dutse mai aman wuta yana zubo toka a birnin Mexico
Tashin toka da dutsen Popocatapetl ya zubo ya kai kudancin Mexico City.
Cibiyar rigakafin bala'i ta kasa a ranar Asabar ta gargadi 'yan Mexico da su guji kusanci da dutsen mai aman wuta bayan da aka samu karin aiki a cikin ramin kuma an samu fitar da gas da toka 183 a cikin sa'o'i 24.
Cibiyar ta lura da yawan rawar jiki da rawar jiki.
Hotunan da aka wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna wasu laka a kan gilashin mota a unguwannin birnin Mexico kamar Xochimilco.
Masana ilimin ƙasa sun lura da ƙaruwar ayyukan dutsen mai fitad da wuta da ke da nisan mil 45 daga kudu maso gabashin babban birnin ƙasar tun lokacin da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.1 ta girgiza tsakiyar Mexico a shekara ta 2017.
Wani dutse mai fitad da wuta da ake kira Don Goyo ya fara aiki tun shekara ta 1994.
'Yan sanda da 'yan adawar Catalonia sun yi arangama a ranar tunawa da zaben neman 'yancin kai
An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai sun yi arangama da 'yan sanda da suka shiga cikin lamarin kuma bayan dubban mutane sun shiga zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewa da zaben raba gardama na Catalonia.
Wasu 'yan tawaye da suka yi ado da kayan ado da suka nemi gafara daga 'yan sanda sun soma jefa ƙwai da kuma fentin foda a kan 'yan sanda, kuma hakan ya sa aka yi duhu a kan titunan da za su cika da masu yawon buɗe ido.
An sake yin faɗa a ranar da 'yan sanda suka yi amfani da sanduna don su kwantar da hankali.
A cikin sa'o'i da yawa, ƙungiyoyin 'yancin kai sun yi ihu "Ba za a manta da ku ba, ba za a gafarta muku ba", kuma a gefe guda, 'yan ƙungiyar sun yi ihu "Bari Spain ta daɗe".
An kwantar da mutane 14 a asibiti sakamakon raunuka masu saurin gaske da suka samu a zanga-zangar, in ji manema labarai.
Tashin hankali a yankin da ke neman 'yancin kai bai ragu ba shekara guda bayan zaben raba gardama da Madrid ta ayyana a matsayin haramtacce a ranar 1 ga watan Oktoba, wanda 'yan gurguzu na Catalonia ke murna da shi.
Yawancin masu jefa kuri'a sun zabi 'yancin kai duk da cewa yawan masu kada kuri'a kadan ne saboda wadanda ke adawa da raba gari sun fi yawan kauracewa zaben.
A cewar hukumomin Catalonia, kusan mutane 1,000 ne suka ji rauni a rikice-rikicen da aka yi a bara bayan da 'yan sanda suka yi kokarin dakatar da zaben a wuraren zabe a fadin yankin.
Kungiyoyin 'yancin kai sun yi zanga-zanga a daren Juma'a don hana zanga-zangar nuna goyon baya ga 'yan sanda.
An gudanar da zanga-zangar, amma an tilasta wa masu zanga-zangar su bi wata hanya.
Narcis Termes, mai shekaru 68, wani mai aikin lantarki wanda ya halarci zanga-zangar 'yan tawaye tare da matarsa ya ce ba ya fatan Catalonia ta samu 'yancin kai.
A shekarar da ta shige, mun yi farin ciki sosai.
Na ga iyayena suna kuka saboda farin cikin da suka samu na kada kuri'a, amma yanzu mun makale, in ji shi.
Duk da samun gagarumar nasara a zaben yankin da aka yi a watan Disamba, jam'iyyun 'yancin kai na Catalonia suna fama da wahalar ci gaba da samun ci gaba a wannan shekara, yayin da fitattun shugabanninsu ke gudun hijira ko kuma a tsare suna jiran shari'a saboda rawar da suka taka wajen shirya kuri'ar raba gardama da kuma sanar da 'yancin kai.
Joan Puig, wani mai aikin injiniya mai shekara 42 da ke yin fim a wayarsa don nuna goyon bayansa ga 'yan sanda, ya ce 'yan siyasa a bangarorin biyu ne suka haddasa wannan rikici.
Ya ce, "Yanayin ya kara tsauri".
A ranar Asabar Oriol Junqueras, daya daga cikin shuwagabannin Catalonia guda tara da ke tsare a gidan yari tun karshen shekarar da ta gabata ya sanar da cewa zai tsaya takarar zaben majalisar Turai a shekara mai zuwa.
