China ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a ƙasar.
Kimanin sabbin mutane 40,000 ne aka samu a cikin zangon biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtukan cututtuka suna faruwa ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da na baya.
A dā, cutar HIV tana yaduwa da sauri a wasu ɓangarorin ƙasar Sin ta wajen ƙarin jini da ke ɗauke da cutar.
A wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ce babu kusan kowa da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i matsala ce ta dindindin tsakanin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma an ce nuna bambanci ga LGBT mutane yana da yawa.
Bincike ya nuna cewa a ƙasarmu, mutane da yawa sun amince da ra'ayin 'yan Adam kuma hakan ya sa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna aure.
Yawancin cututtuka da ke faruwa a cikin irin wannan dangantaka suna faruwa ne saboda rashin kariya a lokacin jima'i.
A shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta ba da maganin cutar HIV a ko'ina.
