A cikin fim din Johnny English: Sakewa a kan aikin Rowan Atkinson mai ban sha'awa ba ya yaki da ɗan leƙen asiri
Yanzu abu ne da ya zama ruwan dare gama gari ga kowane sabon fim din Burtaniya don neman saƙonnin Brexit, kuma da alama haka lamarin yake a sabon fim ɗin wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English wanda aka fara shi a 2003 kuma ya dawo kan manyan allon 2011 mai taken Johnny English Rides Again.
Shin wannan baƙar magana game da yadda muke da ƙima za ta zama sabuwar hanyar fitar da kaya ta ƙasa?
Johnny English mara iya magana, mai idanu masu launin toka da fuska mai launin roba yana da izini don sake rikitar da al'amuran, yayin da sunansa ya ce fiye da komai cewa wannan zane ne na zane-zane ga masu sauraro da aka tsara don ƙasashen da ba a yin fim ba a Turanci.
Shi ne, ba shakka, wani dan leken asiri wanda duk da cewa yana da kyawawan dabi'u na "mai ban sha'awa" yana kama da Inspector Clouseau, yana da ɗan Mr. Bean kuma yana da ɗan ɗan gajeren lokaci wanda ya rera waƙar da ke buɗewa "Chariots of Fire" a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
Halinsa kuma ya samo asali ne daga matafiyi da kuma wani mutum mai ban mamaki wanda Atkinson ya taba yi a cikin tallace-tallace na TV da aka manta da su yanzu don Barclaycard kuma wanda yake nuna rikici.
Akwai wani abu mai kyau ko biyu a cikin wannan sabon fim ɗin.
Na ji daɗin ganin Johnny English yana zuwa jirgi mai saukar ungulu sanye da kayan dāga na dā kuma ya ji kamar an buga kwalkwali a kan shi.
Ana iya ganin baiwar Atkinson don wasan kwaikwayo na jiki, amma wasan kwaikwayo yana da ban sha'awa sosai kuma ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman ma yanzu da manyan fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suna ba da kayan wasan kwaikwayo.
A ganina, ba a taɓa ganin irin wannan ƙarancin Johnny English ba kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a matsayin Mr. Bean.
Wannan ra'ayin cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala mai tsanani ya zama sananne.
Wani dan leken asiri ya shiga cikin babbar hanyar leken asiri ta yanar gizo ta Burtaniya kuma ya gano ainihin duk jami'an Burtaniya, abin takaici ga jami'in da ke aiki, wanda rashin alheri ga ɗan gajeren lokaci Kevin Eldon ya yi.
Wannan ya zubar da gilashin haƙurin Firayim Minista, mai girman kai da son faɗa wanda ke fuskantar cikakken rushewar tsarin saboda ƙiyayya ta siyasa: Emma Thompson tana ƙoƙari ta nuna ainihin mutumin da ya kamata ya wakilci Theresa May amma ba ta sami kayan aiki da za a yi da shi ba.
Masu ba da shawara kan harkokin leken asiri sun bayyana mata cewa duk 'yan leken asiri da ke aiki sun lalace kuma saboda haka dole ne ta sake gyara tsohon jami'in.
Kuma wannan mutumin zai zama Johnny English mai ban tsoro wanda a halin yanzu yake aiki a matsayin darektan wata makarantar sakandare, amma a asirce yana koyar da yadda za a zama wakili na sirri: akwai wasu kyawawan abubuwa a nan saboda English yana koyar da leken asiri na rock.
