A wannan Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara tare da jerin taurari masu ban sha'awa da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa  kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai a jere, bikin Global Citizen Festival zai tara dubban mutane a Central Park don ba kawai jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon taurari kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron, don kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci nan da shekarar 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na aikin Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta duniya da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan ba su yarda su biya VIP ba), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayon dole ne su yi wasu ayyuka ko ayyuka kamar yin aikin sa kai, aika imel ga shugaban duniya, yin kira ta waya, ko kuma wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don wayar da kan jama'a game da manufarsu ta kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar Global Citizen yake idan aka yi la'akari da cewa yana da shekaru 12 da ya rage don cimma burin?
Shin kyautar kyauta kyauta ce hanya madaidaiciya ta tabbatar da mutane su nemi kira zuwa aiki, ko kuma wani misali ne na kira da ake kira "clicktivism" inda mutane ke jin cewa ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takardar neman taimako ta yanar gizo ko aika tweet da gaske suna kawo canji?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ya ce ya samu fiye da Actions miliyan 19 daga magoya bayansa da ke neman cimma wasu manufofi.
Ya ce waɗannan ayyuka sun motsa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da za su kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayukan mutane fiye da biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, rukunin ya ba da lamuni game da alkawura 390 da sanarwar da suka samo asali daga ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka biya ko aka tara.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya sun sami damar yin amfani da kudaden da aka tanada.
Wasu daga cikin muhimman alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta masu saka jari da masu shirya shirye-shirye a Burtaniya da ke da niyyar taimaka wa yara su bunkasa zuwa cikakkiyar damar su, tare da alkawarin cewa bayan karbar tweets sama da 4,700 daga 'yan kasa da kasa, za su samar da dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa Rwanda wajen kawo karshen matsalar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a yankin.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin kasa da na duniya, za mu iya kawo karshen rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihi", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition Foundation, ga masu sauraro a wani biki a Landan a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma bayyana cewa bayan ayyuka sama da 5000 da aka dauka don inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga uwaye da yara, Gwamnati ta sanar da samar da kudade don aikin The Power of Nutrition wanda zai samar da taimakon abinci ga mata da yara miliyan 5.
A amsa ga wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a shafinsa, "Me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
