Jihohi 18 da D.C. sun goyi bayan sake duba sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan kalubalantar sabuwar manufar Amurka ta hana masu fama da aikata laifuka da kuma tashin hankali daga gida mafaka.
Wakilan jihohi da gundumomi 18 sun gabatar da rahoto mai kyau a ranar Juma'a a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka wanda ke kalubalantar manufofin, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da kara ba a cikin karar Grace da Sessions da kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta kan manufofin tarayya.
Ta ce abokin aikinta da wasu 'yan daba masu zafin rai sun ci zarafinta, amma jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da bukatar da ta yi na neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
