A cikin jawabinsa ga Radio 4 Desert Island Disks, wanda Lauren Laverne ke jagoranta, ya ce yana magana ne game da 'yancin' yan luwadi don ya ba wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce nasararsa a gasar Olympics ba ta da muhimmanci tun da ya zama uba.
Kirsty Young, wadda ta daɗe tana nuna shirin, ta ɗauki wasu watanni ba ta aiki don rashin lafiya.
Bayan ya fito a matsayin mai watsi da Laverne na farko, Daley ya ce a lokacin da yake girma ya ji "ba shi da daraja" idan aka kwatanta da sauran saboda "ba a yarda da shi a cikin zamantakewa don son yara maza da mata ba".
