Daley ya auri wani ɗan wasan Oscar wanda ya girme shi da shekara 20 a shekarar da ta shige, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taɓa zama matsala ba.
"Yayin da kake matashi kana fuskantar matsaloli masu yawa", ya tuna lokacin da ya fara gasar Olympics sa'ad da yake ɗan shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu sanadiyyar ciwon daji bayan shekara uku, ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya da ya fuskanci irin wannan matsala.
