Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda an katse sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga lardin Donggale ba, yankin da ke arewacin Palua wanda ya fi kusa da mahaifar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palu bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Palu da Donggala, a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne, wanda ke ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙanƙanin ƙauye a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala shi ne gundumar da ke da nisan kilomita 300 a gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin shekarar 2017, an kiyasta yawan jama'ar yankin 299 200.
A cikin wannan yanki, akwai wasu yankuna da ke da yawan kifi da kuma kiwo.
Ma'adinan nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi suna cikin Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a garin Donggala.
Tsunami kuma ya auku a yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Fasifik kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004. Girgizar ƙasa mai girma a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi a Aceh.
2005: An yi wata guguwa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Niasu, a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006. Girgizar ƙasa mai girman maki 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi girma a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya auku a gabar teku ta kudu, kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afka wa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 30 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016. Girgizar kasa mai zurfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haddasa lalacewa da firgici domin ta tunatar da mutane da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta auku a 2004.
Amma, mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu sa'ad da ginin ya faɗi.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok da ke ƙasar Indonesia, ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta hana dubban masu yawon bude ido zuwa wurin.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin iyalansa
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska da kuma mataimakin shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, an kama shi ne bisa zargin hari.
Palin, mai shekaru 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, an kama shi ne bisa zargin cin zarafin mata, hana bayar da rahoton cin zarafin mata da kuma tsayayya da kama shi, a cewar rahoton da aka fitar a ranar Asabar daga jami'an 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya nuna cewa, sa'ad da wata abokiyarta ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don ta kai ƙarar laifin, sai ya ƙwace wayarta.
Palin yana tsare a gidan yarin Mat-Su kuma an tsare shi a kan takardar kudi ta dala 500, rahoton KTUU.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu ranar Asabar, inda ya amsa tambayar da aka yi masa game da laifinsa, ya ce "ba shi da laifi, ba shakka", in ji kafafen yada labarai.
An tuhumi Palina da laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin cewa zai iya yin shekara guda a kurkuku da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda ake yi da ranar guda a kurkuku da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka kai karar Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an tuhume shi da laifin kai hari kan mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton zargin cewa an yi mata fyade.
Ana gabatar da wannan shari'ar ne a kotun soja a Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin mata, hana kai rahoton cin zarafin mata da kuma mallakar bindiga a cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta ce ya buge ta a fuska.
Kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji sun soki Sarah Palin a shekarar 2016 bayan ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da PTSD bayan aikinsa a Iraki.
