Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York.
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun nemi a yankewa Sayful Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin kisa da ba a taba yankewa ba a jihar tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da wata motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan hanyar West Side a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da kekuna da suka shiga hanyarsa a watan Oktoba
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya "da gangan" ya kashe mutane takwas da kuma "da gangan" ya yi mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar game da niyyar neman hukuncin kisa, wanda aka gabatar a gundumar kudu ta New York.
Duk waɗannan abubuwan biyu suna haifar da yiwuwar hukuncin kisa, bisa ga takardar shari'a.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke hukunci kan zargin Saipov da lambobi 22 wanda ya hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai da cin zarafi, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su a lokuta masu rikitarwa, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "tsari mai kyau da kuma tunani", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna mai bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi shi a matsayin "mummunan, mummunan aiki da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi sanadiyyar raunuka, lalacewa da asarar rayuka ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Hernán Ferruchi, Hernán Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Pagnucca", in ji sanarwar da aka bayar.
Wadanda aka kashe biyar daga cikin su 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shude tun lokacin da gundumar kudu ta New York ta yi shari'ar hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan wasu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma an yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
An yi hukuncin kisa a kan wani mutum a New York a shekara ta 1953 lokacin da aka kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg da kuma Rosenberg a kan 19 ga Yuni, 1953, a cikin kujera ta lantarki.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin tuba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa yana jin dadi game da abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa bayan da ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, ya samu wahayi don kai harin, in ji tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi a rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan abubuwa 22 da ake tuhumarsa da su.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi takaicin hukuncin da ake tuhumarsu da shi.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin rai da rai a gidan yari ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba, zai kara haifar da wata cuta ga duk wanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
