"Ba zan iya guje wa tunanin cewa mace, idan ta taɓa yin hakan, za a kira ta 'mai saurin fushi'", in ji Pelosi game da yadda ta amsa shaidar Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa a ranar Alhamis.
Kavanaugh ya musanta zargin cewa ya yi wa Dr. Christine Blasey Ford fyade lokacin da suke matasa.
A lokacin jawabinsa na farko, Kavanaugh ya kasance mai matukar damuwa, a wasu lokuta yana kusan ihu da kuma nutsuwa yayin da yake tattaunawa game da iyalinsa da shekarun makarantar sakandare.
