Yadda yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama mai kyau ga Beijing
An yi ta faɗakarwa game da farawar yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, kuma yayin da yakin ya yi nisa da ƙarshe, rikice-rikice tsakanin ƙasashen na iya amfanar Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara ba da gargadin farko a farkon wannan shekarar, ya sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, ciki har da allon hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminum.
Babban tashin hankali a wannan makon ya zo ne da sabbin haraji da suka shafi kayayyaki masu darajar dala biliyan 200, a zahiri suna biyan rabin dukkan kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
A kowane lokaci, Beijing tana ramawa, kuma kwanan nan ta saka haraji tsakanin kashi biyar zuwa kashi goma bisa dala biliyan 60 na kayayyakin Amirka.
China ta yi alkawarin mayar da hari ga Amurka, kuma tattalin arzikinta na biyu mafi girma a duniya ba zai yi kasa a gwiwa ba.
Za a iya samun janyewar Washington ta hanyar sassauta buƙatun, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi wasa da katunan ta, matsin lamba daga yakin cinikin Amurka na iya ba da tallafi mai kyau ga China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa yanke shawara na siyasa cikin sauri a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai haifar da rushewar tattalin arziki a ƙasashen biyu ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu lura suka yi imani", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike kan dabarun tunani wanda ya mai da hankali kan Asiya a Cibiyar Sabon Tsaron Amurka.
Syria ta "shirya" don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira, in ji ministan harkokin waje
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina ƙasar da yaƙi ya halaka fiye da shekara bakwai.
Da yake jawabi ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin ƙasar yana samun ci gaba.
Ya ce, "Yanzu yanayin a filin ya fi karko da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci".
Gwamnati na ci gaba da aikin gyara yankunan da hare-haren ta'addanci ya lalata don dawo da al'amura na yau da kullun.
Yanzu an cika dukkan sharuddan don dawowar 'yan gudun hijirar cikin yardar rai zuwa kasar da suka tsere saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na kai tsaye wanda aka mayar da hankali kan rayuwarsu ta yau da kullun da kuma rayuwa.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa 'yan Syria sama da miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a shekarar 2011.
Mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar na bukatar agajin jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria na bukatar taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Ya ce ba zai amince da tallafin da aka tanadar masa ba ko kuma na kasashen da suka tallafa wa 'yan tawayen.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta Paris
Tawagar Turai ta yi nasara a gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018, ta doke tawagar Amurka da ci 16.5 ̶ 10.5 a filin wasa na Le Golf National kusa da Paris, Faransa.
Amurka ta sha kaye har sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin yayin da tawagar Denmark ta Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata don cin Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a kusan dukkanin gasar, a rami na 16 na uku, ya jefa kwallon cikin ruwa a karo na farko, ya ba da wasan ga Francesco Molinari.
